# questkit-worker-demo — local dev secrets.
#
# The demo worker proxies a single endpoint (POST /api/token) to the real
# api worker at https://api.questkit.jairukchan.com/v1/auth/token, passing
# APP_SECRET on behalf of the browser so the secret never reaches the
# client. The value here MUST match the APP_SECRET set on
# questkit-worker-api (see workers/api/.dev.vars.example).
#
# Locally `wrangler dev` loads this file (rename to .dev.vars). In prod set
# via `wrangler secret put APP_SECRET --name questkit-worker-demo`.
#
# generate: openssl rand -base64 48
APP_SECRET=
